sentences.english: Adjust the density (amount of ink) of the print.
sentences.chinese: 調整打印時墨點的密度。

sentences.english: This week on the gadget Show, we find out what the best printers on the market are.
sentences.chinese: 在本週的小器具展上我們發現了市場上最好的打印機。

sentences.english: The other major innovation in this example is the use of formatted printing.
sentences.chinese: 本例中的另一項主要創新是使用了格式化打印。

sentences.english: Print monetary and nonmonetary determinations (407 and 410).
sentences.chinese: 打印貨幣或非貨幣決定。

sentences.english: These printouts are sometimes referred to as hard copy.
sentences.chinese: 這種打印輸出有時也被稱爲硬拷貝。

sentences.english: The test code at the bottom then sets the value and prints out the new value.
sentences.chinese: 底部的測試代碼設置值並打印出新值。

sentences.english: I stared at the sheets of paper lying facedown on the printer.
sentences.chinese: 我盯着打印機裏面朝下擱着的一摞紙。

sentences.english: Email involves attachments, and users need to print files that they receive.
sentences.chinese: 電子郵件可能包含附件，用戶需要打印接收的文件。

sentences.english: Everything from prothetic limbs to pre-fabricated houses will be made using similar printing technology.
sentences.chinese: 從醫用假肢到預製房屋，3D打印技術可謂無處不在。

sentences.english: In the first article, my goal was to obtain printable reports.
sentences.chinese: 在第一篇文章中，我的目的是得到可打印報表。

sentences.english: Please, print it and put stamps and signatures of Beiji company.
sentences.chinese: 請把它打印出來並簽上你們公司的章。

sentences.english: Look no further for all your printable calender needs.
sentences.chinese: 你再看看所有打印壓延需要。

sentences.english: The computer software will allow you to print labels whenever you wish.
sentences.chinese: 電腦軟件可以打印出任何你需要的品牌。

sentences.english: Kerning is only available for certain font types and, for printed documents, only works if your printer supports it.
sentences.chinese: 這選項是否有效取決於使用的字體和打印機是否支持。

sentences.english: Lanie, I'm going to print more printers.
sentences.chinese: 拉妮，我打算印出更多的三維打印機。

sentences.english: To change a printer to print upper-case letters(and various symbols) instead of lower-case.
sentences.chinese: 印刷或打印用的一種小寫字符。
